Package cc.carm.lib.easysql.api

Interface SQLBuilder

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConditionalBuilder<B,​T>, DeleteBuilder, QueryBuilder, TableAlterBuilder, TableCreateBuilder, TableMetadataBuilder, TableQueryBuilder, UpdateBuilder
    public interface SQLBuilder
    SQLBuilder 是用于构建SQL语句以生成SQLAction执行操作的中间类。
    其连接了SQLManager 与 SQLAction ,避免大量的代码堆积
    也是本接口的核心功能所在
    Author:
    CarmJos
